duces\nthe cluster mass function, making it a valuable tool for employing cluster\nobservations to evaluate cosmological models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2015 20:14:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2016 14:10:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-09"}
