46 could be magnetospheric,\nimplying a mass accretion rate of a few 10^-7 Msun/yr. This value indicates\nthat the observed gas has to be replenished on time-scales of a few months to\nyears, perhaps by planet-induced flows from the outer to the inner disc as has\nbeen reported for similar systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2015 20:14:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-21"}
