e the same expectation\nfor the canonical statistic. To allow for estimators taking values outside of\nthe exponential family, we include results for KL projection and define an\nextended projection to accommodate the non-existence of the MLE for families\nhaving discrete sample space. Illustrative examples are provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2015 10:21:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-21"}
