 of\nthe spatial potential profile and show that it is not notable up to biases V\nsomewhat larger than V_t, unlike at higher biases, where it may be responsible\nfor negative differential resistance effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2015 15:09:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-21"}
